<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #667eea; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
    .highlight-box { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; border-radius: 5px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #667eea; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to TalkieToys! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi<% if @subscription.name.present? %> <%= @subscription.name %><% end %>!</h2>

      <p>Welcome to the TalkieToys community! We're thrilled to have you on board.</p>

      <p>You're now subscribed to receive expert insights, practical tips, and valuable resources to support your child's speech development journey.</p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <h3>What to Expect:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Weekly Tips:</strong> Practical speech therapy activities you can do at home</li>
          <li><strong>Product Guides:</strong> Recommendations for age-appropriate speech toys</li>
          <li><strong>Milestone Updates:</strong> Track your child's progress with expert guidance</li>
          <li><strong>Exclusive Resources:</strong> Free worksheets, checklists, and guides</li>
          <li><strong>Success Stories:</strong> Inspiring journeys from other parents</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Here are some resources to get you started:</p>

      <center>
        <a href="<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %>/blog" class="button">Explore Our Blog</a>
        <a href="<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %>/resources" class="button">Browse Resources</a>
      </center>

      <p>Have questions or need help? Simply reply to this email and our team will be happy to assist you!</p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px;">
          <strong>Manage Your Preferences:</strong><br>
          You can update your subscription preferences or unsubscribe at any time by clicking <a href="<%= @unsubscribe_url %>">here</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for trusting us to be part of your child's speech development journey!</p>

      <p>
        Warm regards,<br>
        The TalkieToys Team
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> TalkieToys. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="<%= @unsubscribe_url %>" style="color: #666;">Unsubscribe</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
